Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Largest Mixed-Use Development in Eden Prairie!

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Welcome to Eden Prairie - recognized year after year as one of the best places to live, work and play. The city boosts 37 parks, 17 lakes, and 200 miles of sidewalks and trails. The city has new housing developments underway, both single and multi-family, with more than 5,100 units under construction.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Everything you need is here at Flagship Corporate Center! The building features an outdoor patio overlooking natural wetlands, an abundance of natural light, and a beautiful atrium style lobby overlooking the stunning view.
